item.title: AspireCTF Web Challenge
item.description: Introduction This is a writeup on the Web Challenge of the Aspire CTF - 2021. AgentX Challenge Description: Where are you from? Challenge site The paste contained the ips below 62.210.105.116 51.77.135.89 171.25.193.78 171.25.193.20 185.220.101.208 171.25.193.77 185.165.168.229 185.220.102.8 162.247.72.199 107.189.10.27 106.12.102.21 Following the access link, there is a PHP page that displays the IP address and errors out, Invalid Access! We can try to find out how developers access the IP address of a client.
